concepts.name: Chapter
concepts.context: Indicates a section of the document, denoted by '#' and '##' markdown headers.

concepts.name: Title
concepts.context: The main heading of the document.

hierarchy.structure: The document is structured hierarchically with a main title ('#') followed by a series of numbered chapters ('##'). Some chapters are further subdivided with their own sub-chapter numbering ('###'). This indicates a sequential and organized division of content.
